437
00:30:20,965 --> 00:30:21,965
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Itu semua karenamu.</i></font>

438
00:30:21,965 --> 00:30:23,304
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kau tak punya lensa kontak?</i></font>

439
00:30:23,304 --> 00:30:25,135
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Apa aku terlihat berbeda tanpa kacamata?
Apa kau jatuh cinta padaku lagi?</i></font>

440
00:30:25,135 --> 00:30:26,235
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Bukankah kasus itu sudah berakhir?</i></font>

441
00:30:26,235 --> 00:30:27,235
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku membukanya kembali.</i></font>

442
00:30:27,434 --> 00:30:28,875
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku akan menggalinya sampai akhir.</i></font>

443
00:30:28,905 --> 00:30:30,974
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kenapa sulit berharap banyak?</i></font>

444
00:30:30,974 --> 00:30:32,744
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Itu artinya kau akan kecewa kalau kau gagal.</i></font>

445
00:30:32,744 --> 00:30:35,474
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kenapa kau tidak ingin mengecewakanku?</i></font>

446
00:30:35,474 --> 00:30:37,114
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Nam Hong Joo-ssi, apa yang biasa kau lakukan?</i></font>

447
00:30:37,114 --> 00:30:38,545
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kau tertarik padaku?</i></font>

448
00:30:38,545 --> 00:30:39,885
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Itu artinya kita memulai sesuatu?</i></font>

